sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant API as Feed API
  participant C as Feed Cache
  participant DB as Post Store
  U->>API: GET /feed
  API->>C: read cached feed
  alt cache hit
    C-->>API: post ids
  else miss
    API->>DB: generate feed
    DB-->>API: posts
    API->>C: cache result
  end
  API-->>U: ranked feed
